Walter White and Jesse Pinkman find themselves in a strange early 2000's animated world! What would happen if Breaking Bad met The Fairly Oddparents!

Storyboard and character design help:
https://twitter.com/draws_nerd

Sprite animation at the end by Gaem_On:
https://twitter.com/_gaem_0n

Music help by Moola Mixtape:
https://www.youtube.com/@MoolaMixtape

This was definitely my hardest video to make yet. I'm so happy with how the intro came out!
